IO

Class JmzReaderAdaptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • IO.JmzReaderAdaptor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Iterator

    public class JmzReaderAdaptor
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Iterator
    This class provide a adapting interface to use the jmzReader interface, converting spectrum object from the jmzReader framework to our own spectrum data object. Since the jmzReader support several standard format, we use their parser instead of the one build-in msplit to extends the support of query format. However for reading annotated spectrum format, the standard interface of jzmReader does not yet fully support, need to add in these features of use the SpectrumReader for loading those file
    Author:
    Jian
